node.text: I mentioned @bondiboost a while back and since my last post, I’m a red head and I currently have extensions. This brand was helping strengthen my real hair so much that I felt ready to make a drastic and fun change. I’ve been shampooing and conditioning and treating my extensions with Bondi Boost products and all of it has had the most glorious effect on my hair. Everything is of course paraben, silicone, and sulfite free and vegan! I love these products so much and I would highly recommend. Link is in my stories! Use code IRELAND20 at checkout! ♥️✨ #bondiboostus #boostyourroots #ad
